features.text: Level 2 click above -- for Meme Arch Click Below

Graduation Requirements for the School:

-Mint 5 golds,

-Make a sale on Opensea 

-Find a way to get good links better than my tips and tricks (when the student becomes the master)

-Be able to tip another person in Marble Main Discord or PSOM

-Answer questions in general chat 

-Be able to take someone under your wing and teach them our ways. (need an apprentice)

-Commit at least 1 poach (when the poachee becomes the poacher)

-Get stuck in the "remarble hole" (remarble >25x on a card) 

-Earn a badge in any of the arenas

-Bring on a verified artist to Marble.Cards

-Field questions in support channel
How the Marble Machine mints out the cards.

WELCOME TO PATZO'S SCHOOL OF MARBLING

-If you like what you see, please join us in the meme.com/marblecards Discord Server here=  https://discord.gg/4VEpbWbz

You can also DM Patzo on Twitter or in Discord to get a special Invite into PSOM.

We are a strong community driven side project that offers extra rewards to new marblers and OG marblers alike!

Our Founder Patzo, has gone above and beyond for this community and his students and will continue to do so for each one of us. 

Drop by and say hi, we look forward to chatting with you. Oh and if you have not yet tried to marble a card... you are missing out, it's so much fun and there is also ways to earn extra income inside the world of marblecards, you can marble a youtube link and then battle it against other cards for astronomy.com for example. It's all about the marbling.

The fun doesn't stop there, we also have a really cool card ame called MarbleClash where two members go head-to-head with a deck of 10 cards they own (or now a demo deck can be used) battling cards by throwing a card with a specific requirement. ASK US HOW TODAY!!!!
